ActorTimeLine - Class in movieproject
ActorTimeLine is essentially a wrapper for the PersonCredits class that uses a TmdbMovies object to all the retrieval of additional categories of info, such as the revenue generated by a referenced by a film in an actor's PersonCredits.
ActorTimeLine(PersonCredits, TmdbMovies) - Constructor for class movieproject.ActorTimeLine
Constructor uses credits and tmdb movies object to create a PersonCredits wrapper that uses the movies object to allow accessing additional info.
